title: Python
description:
Python is a high-level, interpreted, versatile programming language. Its design prioritizes code readability through significant indentation. Python is dynamically typed and features garbage collection.
  
      Explore further at the following resources:
      
      - [Official Website: Python](https://www.python.org/)
      - [Tutorial Series: How to Code in Python](https://www.python.org/about/gettingstarted/)
      - [Python Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Python_(programming_language))
      - [Google's Python Class](https://developers.google.com/edu/python/)
      - [W3Schools - Python Tutorial](https://www.w3schools.com/python/)
